{"tid":2041892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[Twitter戰線]香港人再一次展現咩叫手足","createTime":"2020-05-29T13:37:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T14:19:29.000Z","uid":170426,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"315487c26965be39e832350c1257c0cbb1e9aa3a","tid":2041892,"uid":170426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T13:37:04.000Z","msg":"當英國開始吹風要俾BNO holders有居英權，好多手足提到相比起居英權，我地更加關心一班冇BNO但出心出力甚至為香港民主自由奉上鮮血嘅手足<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/iowbobseely/status/1266081608672727041?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fiowbobseely%2Fstatus%2F1266081608672727041%3Fs%3D21&d=nsl8wma01YyMGEZOa9B33EVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=e257b1d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fiowbobseely%2Fstatus%2F1266081608672727041%3Fs%3D21&h=80d2c581\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/iowbobseely/status/1266081608672727041?s=21</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zbuzw7k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZbuzw7k.png&h=c090b151&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mj0ZJd1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmj0ZJd1.png&h=68e0584a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Q1uk0G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Q1uk0G.png&h=dd2899bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢幾幅圖只係由上面條tweet cap出黎，仲有好多tweet都有手足展現團結嘅comment<br />\n<br />\n五毛以為用BNO可以分化我地<br />\n多謝香港人再一次展現咩叫<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">手足</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"2b1cd1dc0e1459037cd7aa70cd08f3123ede3d88","tid":2041892,"uid":170426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T13:37:26.000Z","msg":"香港獨立 唯一出路"},{"pid":"4174380b45f5a8cf82875ec111675a9f2c28e986","tid":2041892,"uid":170426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T13:37:50.000Z","msg":"香港獨立 唯一出路"},{"pid":"f8a3277c60f